{"tid":784740,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍拖紀念日重唔重要？","createTime":"2018-08-18T15:32:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T11:37:56.000Z","uid":40518,"like":33,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"daef1843b211762384e904694920dc156a1f6d69","tid":784740,"uid":40518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T15:32:56.000Z","msg":"唔係話每個月都要慶祝<br />\n但男女朋友應該至少記得呢個日子，當日起碼都講句&rdquo;happy xx months&rdquo; 掛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我同我男朋友一齊左年幾，佢一次都冇主動同我講過，有幾次甚至我講佢都唔應我<br />\n其實呢個日子係咪應該重視下呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁重要嘅日子應該記得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 算吧啦咪又係普通一日"},{"pid":"653550526f6d687a02a62a14a2765051e0732f34","tid":784740,"uid":138981,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T15:35:08.000Z","msg":"每對couple都有自己嘅共識同習慣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你覺得要重視啲咪同佢講<br />\n<br />\n利申不嬲乜紀念日節日都唔慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ea038ac9bba4b0f0caa56322c46e507f3f2f55","tid":784740,"uid":66321,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T16:13:33.000Z","msg":"以前同男朋友每個月都會慶祝<br />\n過左第一年之後就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知點解大家都成日唔記得<br />\n無特別話慶祝lu<br />\n係一年半個時先有記起<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9815f1dfbf7b306c29af153dd6783d55ffbdf1","tid":784740,"uid":29335,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T16:22:09.000Z","msg":"每個月都要紀念？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得拍拖紀念周年就應該重視既<br />\n每個月都講一次就誇張咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申絲"},{"pid":"23bf81fcc9bb60bec1a965c2213ac851acf102f4","tid":784740,"uid":82414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T16:25:08.000Z","msg":"周年紀念日就話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每個月都固定講好誇張<br />\n記得都可能會講嘅<br />\n利申 絲"},{"pid":"013dc481e9cca517b3e54f8f7352e84d8523fe87","tid":784740,"uid":4382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T16:26:06.000Z","msg":"當你拍咗年半以上<br />\n你就發現講唔講都冇分別 更加唔會特別過<br />\n拍咗拖3年 頭半年咪個個月講一句<br />\n到後期已經係一年都懶得慶祝一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3980f2084a4867e469c055d2456182e60a17d5a7","tid":784740,"uid":40518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:41:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4218789b2cf5f63a866af01821b66a175c4f07df","tid":784740,"uid":28800,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:46:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"65e8e89faef646fee6f18ae886b3fb05edb2c251","tid":784740,"uid":2479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T16:25:27.000Z","msg":"周年紀念我覺得點都要嘅<br />\n始終係嗰一日大家有共識決定喺埋一齊 係人生一個特別嘅日子<br />\n可能會食好啲咁 <br />\n<br />\n啲x個月我哋覺得唔重要 都冇刻意去記<br />\n過吓過吓就一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b138ae6003bf9997d7525d27182c0c5a4ddbfe","tid":784740,"uid":2786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T16:27:19.000Z","msg":"拍左拖兩年幾三年<br />\n已經唔鬼會慶祝週月紀念日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲下三週年果日要實習 我諗都慶祝唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770fc2bea5cc57859807ba78e04e836815198e32","tid":784740,"uid":149357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T01:51:46.000Z","msg":"每個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e137637e8efe18848818d81eecbd6b3648b899","tid":784740,"uid":140798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T01:54:44.000Z","msg":"痴撚線啦 一定記得 點一齊都記得啦<br />\n唔記得真係無乜心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4313411890b39ba8a5765f28f7881ddeba767776","tid":784740,"uid":91897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:12:26.000Z","msg":"每月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  記得都唔會慶祝啦, 講下XX月快樂咪算<br />\n<br />\n周年就會慶祝啦"},{"pid":"1ba063c15b02dd42d812d2809ccc81ad48df7313","tid":784740,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:16:36.000Z","msg":"我覺得唔駛慶祝<br />\n但有心思記得係好sweet"},{"pid":"2f7dc308322a0ac24f6e0c56667091ad4443e767","tid":784740,"uid":97439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ba063c15b02dd42d812d2809ccc81ad48df7313","tid":784740,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:16:36.000Z","msg":"我覺得唔駛慶祝<br />\n但有心思記得係好sweet"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:19:19.000Z","msg":"同意 唔洗特別約/plan慶祝<br />\n偷偷地買份禮物 book間k房 之類仲sweet"},{"pid":"45dd197ba7cb935fd8e8e8f1b4dd8da34bcea500","tid":784740,"uid":179990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:22:25.000Z","msg":"頭嗰年都有慶祝過嘅 之後都口頭講句就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6bd42d23e5a9708b6aca87990d67afc669014e4","tid":784740,"uid":89348,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T11:37:56.000Z","msg":"如果週年紀念都會唔記得 你自己同自己慶祝算啦 佢根本冇重視過呢段情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}